{
  "texts": [
    "For example, the number 3 in the first row and second column indicated that three students from that dormitory entered or exited the library on Tuesday.",
    "These visual representations were crucial in helping participants understand the practical task at hand-to utilize ChatGPT and the provided data along with the Matplotlib library to draw a stacked bar chart that visualizes the entry and exit records of these five dormitories from Monday to Friday more intuitively.",
    "With this contextual information, participants were officially instructed to commence the practical phase, with a time limit of 50 min to complete the task.",
    "Step 5: Post-test and project effectiveness evaluation.",
    "After completing the programming project task, participants submitted their practical outcomes (stacked bar charts) through an online platform (a sample of project outcomes is shown in Fig. 3)."
  ]
